title: Johnson & Johnson 's net income 2005 to 2019
yAxis: Net income in million U.S. dollars
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Net income in million U.S. dollars, containing a total of 15 data points.
Overall Net income in million U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
Net income in million U.S. dollars is roughly constant from 2005 to 2016, roughly increasing from 2016 to 2018, and finally roughly constant from 2018 to 2019.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2016 and 2017.
Maximum Net income in million U.S. dollars, about 16540.0 was reported at Year 2016
The lowest Net income in million U.S. dollars, of value 1300.0 was reported at Year 2017
